{
  "stem": "8784.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Some occasions like that would have been when there was some unloading of trains to be-- to be done, they would come in and round up some people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This was true.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But this was so rare that it really was entirely different than the life we had in Krakow-Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was food in a better supply.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "At work, we were in peace.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Somehow Schindler was always present there, and we somehow felt that there is a mantle of-- Schindler's mantle protecting us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were working together at the factory with some non-Jews who would be arriving from the outside of Krakow to work in the factory.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we were the inmates of this camp, but we did work together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I remember working for a fellow who was a-- a carpenter, a cabinet maker.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He was my boss inside the Emalia works, and his-- this Polish Christian was a fellow by the name of Wuczek.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I-- I-- from then on, I begin to work as a carpenter, a cabinet maker.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I have gained some experience in that field before I even entered the ghetto when I worked for this fellow-- for a fellow by the name of Kaminski in-- before I entered the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It's the one I described where he was willing to keep me over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And so my work now was as a carpenter in that newly created camp. 1,000 of us lived there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "My duties took me to Oskar Schindler's offices because one of my jobs was to maintain the darkout or blackout shades.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I would have to see to it that they were in good working order, because when the-- when the airplanes would come over Krakow for bombing missions, these darkout shades would be pulled down.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So they always had to be in good working.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
